"taste is a little dank. a bit sweet like a dopple, some wheat in there, but certainly not of the same quality of many of its german counterparts. it's not bad, it's actually good, but I think the dank, mustiness of the aroma is a huge turnoff as that is the first tactile sense one gets..."
